		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Another cool idea (perhaps impossible I dunno...) would be a software-pause mode sort of.
<br />Imagine pressing a certain combination of buttons to switch back to BIOS menu to pick a new game, or, perhaps being able to browse/edit RAM (for simple hacking purposes perhaps).

		

